            <sentence>
                <offset>241</offset>
                <text>He was born to consanguineous parents and there were no other similarly affected family members (Pedigree Fig. 1A).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>357</offset>
                <text>There was a prenatal history of doubtful maternal gestational diabetes and oligohydramnios in the last trimester.</text>
