                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>471</offset>
                <text>Delivery was unremarkable, and the birth weight was 4.5 Kgm (+1.89 SD).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>544</offset>
