                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1397</offset>
                <text>Anthropometric measurements showed tall stature 125.4 cm (+3.61 SD), marked obesity with weight 42.3 Kgm (+11.0 SD) and his head circumference was 53.6 cm (+1.5 SD).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1563</offset>
                <text>Echocardiography was normal.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1592</offset>
                <text>Abdominal ultrasound, brain CT, fundus examination and hearing test were normal.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1673</offset>
                <text>Electroencephalogram (EEG) revealed mild focal left fronto-temporal epileptogenic discharge and brain MRI revealed atrophic changes in the form of dilated ventricle, deep sylvian fissure, and small retro-cerebellar cyst.</text>
