            <sentence>
                <offset>1895</offset>
                <text>Due to the patient's intellectual disability and absence of speech, Adaptive Behaviour Assessment (ABAS-3) was applied to evaluate 10 adaptive areas organized in three main domains (conceptual, social, and practical).</text>
                <annotation id="59">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0001249</infon>
                    <location length="23" offset="21"/>
                    <text>intellectual disability</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="60">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0001344</infon>
                    <location length="17" offset="49"/>
                    <text>absence of speech</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>2113</offset>
                <text>Results showed that the adaptive skills were below average in all evaluated fields.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>2197</offset>
                <text>General Adaptive, Composite (GAC) was below 70.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>2245</offset>
                <text>According to the Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders, Fifth Edition (DSM-V) and the administration of the Childhood Autism Rating Scale (CARS), the patient has moderate autism spectrum disorder (ASD).</text>
                <annotation id="61">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
